# Shared cross-platform working tree: the same checkout is accessed from Unix
# (WSL/NFS) and from native Windows. Force LF for every detected-text file so a
# Windows git (e.g. Git-for-Windows with autocrlf=true) can never rewrite the
# tree to CRLF and desync the Unix side. Binaries are auto-detected and left
# untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
